Description:
   Roll With Blow is an innate passive stance that reflects the Pugilist's
   trained ability to absorb and redirect incoming strikes. Permanently
   applies a dodge bonus (Pugilist level/4) and an armor class improvement
   (-Pugilist level/6). Cannot be trained; improves automatically with
   Pugilist level. Combined with Conditioning and natural unarmed defenses,
   this makes the Pugilist surprisingly durable despite wearing lighter
   protection than warrior classes.
